<item>
            <title>[LU-14742] socklnd: detect link down and mark ni as unusable</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14742</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To help avoid selecting lnet ni which corresponds to a downed ethernet link for sending, add a mechanism for detecting link events in socklnd. On link up/down events, find corresponding ni and set/clear ni_fatal_error_on flag, similar to how o2iblnd does it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
